        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 51–54. Miridiba pilosella (Moser, 1908). 51. Lectotype (MFNB). 52–54. Paralectotypes (MFNB). 51. Habitus in dorsal view. 52–53. Male genitalia. 52. Parameres in dorsal (A) and lateral (B) views. 53. Endophallus and temones in dorsal view. 54. Female genitalia in dorsal view. Scale bars: 51 = 5.0 mm; 52–54 = 1.0 mm." ;
